{"tid":316191,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"被公牛撞飛再刺中，鬥牛士疑吐血傷勢未明","createTime":"2017-07-10T14:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T01:37:18.000Z","uid":30040,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79bc753716899c6419d9c5bea5342c0cbfbffe92","tid":316191,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"西班牙潘普洛納市（Pamplona）目前正舉行奔牛節，有鬥牛士被憤怒的公牛用角刺中，登時血流如注。<br />\n<br />\n鬥牛士被公牛撞上半空後，再遭尖角刺傷，他鮮血直冒表情痛苦。其他鬥牛士馬上上前協助分散公牛注意力，其他人合力將受傷的鬥牛士抬離鬥牛場，他嘴角有一條血痕似是吐過血，暫未知其傷勢如何。<br />\n<br />\n而在同日的鬥牛活動中，另一位鬥牛士騎著馬將矛刺向公牛，但因閃躲不及而遭公牛撞至墮馬。<br />\n<br />\n奔牛節歷時長達一周，第三日的奔牛活動有4名男子因撞倒及跌倒受傷，所幸眾人傷勢輕微。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170710&amp;guid=56936294&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170710%26guid%3D56936294%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=xrBEIkkbOI%2BdwT7Vu8BMYYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=29a8bb7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170710%26guid%3D56936294%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=0d228b78\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170710&amp;guid=56936294&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"6bca09658f30b3262a502b788a953f650ed6f4c5","tid":316191,"uid":42527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"撚牛撚死你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d9a8e89bebbc63b4ed46647a0a7644d768cbf2","tid":316191,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"虐殺動物，抵死"},{"pid":"40b86ce1f2cab98d71efc7451848dd8a3afbf6a4","tid":316191,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"有個試過插穿肺<br />\n抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac30d591f950aad53d40728224005165123a067","tid":316191,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:15:49.000Z","msg":"隻牛好仆街"},{"pid":"038dd580eed6875f0abb47bbb7434c5463bd74ca","tid":316191,"uid":40588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:15:59.000Z","msg":"金獅"},{"pid":"0708a664a5a6af8ad343fdfa5bb2782656f6bc77","tid":316191,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>虐殺動物，抵死</blockquote><br />\nD愛護動物協會人士點解走去批鬥人食狗肉，唔走去西班牙批鬥佢地sm牛牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67bc5aa3e17c045e136a9a9a85cffca80ef92b5","tid":316191,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>虐殺動物，抵死</blockquote><br />\nD愛護動物協會人士點解走去批鬥人食狗肉，唔走去西班牙批鬥佢地sm牛牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地一定會講狗係人類最好朋友唔應該食！"}]}